## 9. Non-Functional Requirements

* Search response time < 2 seconds.
* Resume update enforcement backend-only.
* MCP tool access restricted to verified recruiters.
* API rate limiting to prevent scraping.
* All hiring state changes logged.

---

## 10. Assumptions

* Engineers will value structured discovery.
* Recruiters will pay for verified environment.
* AI-native workflows will increase over time.
* GitHub visibility improves technical credibility.

---

## 11. Risks

1. Cold start problem (two-sided marketplace).
2. Recruiters bypassing platform after discovery.
3. Candidate data scraping.
4. Fake GitHub links.
5. Low recruiter adoption if value unclear.

Mitigation:

* Rate limits.
* Strong verification.
* Clear differentiation.
* Early niche focus if needed.

---

## 12. Success Metrics

Month 1:

* 1,000 candidates
* 100 verified recruiters
* 50 interview invites
* 10 confirmed hires

6 Months:

* ≥ 5% candidate-to-hire conversion
* ≥ 70% recruiter satisfaction score
* < 48 hour recruiter verification time

---

## 13. Positioning Statement

HireAHuman.ai is a verified, AI-assisted hiring platform that enables structured candidate discovery and eliminates resume chaos for tech recruitment.

It is not a job board.

It is hiring infrastructure for the AI-native era.

